Class Employee

java.lang.Object
com.android.Human
com.android.Employee
class Employee
extends Human
subclass of Employee and also has its own overriden equals and hashCode method, if this class had not hashCode or equals method, this class would use the equals and hashCode method of the super Human class To see video tutorial for this section of code Video tutorial For all 177 videos, which cover all the topics in this course go to Complete Course Video Tutorial
